🛠️【Easy-peasy Assembly】Assembling this end table is hassle-free, and all necessary hardware and step-by-step instructions are provided. No matter where the LED nightstand is, the classic color design can match any decoration style of yours!

☎️【What to Do if Some Accessories Missing?】This LED charging nightstand is a perfect gift for your family. reviews.reviewText: Super easy to put together. I assembled it myself with no issues. It’s super cute and great for my room. It seems pretty sturdy so far. I think it’s worth it for the price. I would definitely recommend for small spaces.

reviews.reviewText: This bedside table was worth every penny. It’s easy to assemble. It has a good height. It’s light weight and inexpensive. Most importantly, it gives my room an elegant look.
